title: Shelly Crane (Shelby Fallon), Taking Faith (The Stolen Hearts Se
description:
This series of books was written by Shelby Fallon that actually a pen name of Newyork times best seller author Shelly Crane.
This is the second book.
It's probably the genre of this book made Shelly has to hide with pen name but I think it's a good book and therefore recommended this series for all of my friend.
As always, if you find it at your liking, consider to buy for supporting the Author.
